long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Carta is a course website (carta.stanford.edu) that helps Stanford University students search for courses and plan their quarters/years. However, the native course search has limited power and doesn't support semantic search. The Ten Carta Weeks extension replaces the native search on the Carta website via an injected content script with a powerful, blazing fast, semantic search powered by tenweeks.xyz, a course search engine built by Varun Shenoy.
